headline: Spectrum Joins Meyer Shank Racing for the 109th Running of the Indianapolis 500
summary: Meyer Shank Racing (MSR) today announced that Spectrum, one of the nation's leading broadband connectivity providers, will be the primary sponsor for the No. 66 Honda Indy car driven by Marcus Armstrong for the 109th Indianapolis 500 on Sunday, May 25th.
